# VHS tape for robotmem terminal demo
Output assets/demo.gif
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 880
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "# robotmem — Robot Experience Memory"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "export ROBOTMEM_HOME=/tmp/robotmem-demo PYTHONPATH=src"
Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "python3 assets/demo_script.py"
Enter
Sleep 18s
